hooks.prompt:
Review what this subagent did. Respond with JSON: {"ok": true} or {"ok": false, "reason": "..."}.

If the subagent performed meaningful work (code review, implementation, debugging, architectural analysis) and did NOT update its mental model file in .expertise/models/, respond:
{"ok": false, "reason": "You performed meaningful work but did not update your mental model file in .expertise/models/. Please read your model file, update it with patterns, observations, or learnings from this session, then you may stop."}

If no meaningful work was performed, or the mental model was already updated, respond:
{"ok": true}
